WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:05.299
I think it's time for some new wardrobe.

2
00:00:05.299 --> 00:00:07.419
Follow me.

3
00:00:07.419 --> 00:00:17.710
Please leave, otherwise I will call the police.

4
00:00:17.710 --> 00:00:18.710
Excuse me.

5
00:00:18.710 --> 00:00:20.710
This man here is my husband.

6
00:00:20.710 --> 00:00:22.710
I brought him here to get some new clothes.

7
00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:24.710
Is this how you treat all your customers?

8
00:00:24.710 --> 00:00:27.059
My apologies, ma'am.

9
00:00:27.059 --> 00:00:28.059
Please.

10
00:00:28.059 --> 00:00:29.059
Follow me.

11
00:00:29.059 --> 00:00:32.299
Here you are.

12
00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:39.460
Oh, God, those are Uncle's man. I can't let them see me.

